        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n(2 comments)\n\nLooks good, just a couple of changes. Anxious to get the cli merged in.\n\nRegarding the 1.0 release comment, correct me if I am wrong but the Amsterdam release will be first time the cli project is part of ONAP. So maybe all that is required is to change the tagging to be 1.1-STAGING-latest to align with R1.",
